This dataset is a compilation of publicly available Turkish writings originally created by students and instructors at Bilkent University. The dataset compilation, processing, and distribution tools are provided for academic and research purposes only.

PERMITTED USES:
- Academic research and education
- Non-commercial research projects
- Educational coursework and assignments
- Scientific publications and studies
- Personal learning and experimentation

