DISCLAIMER:
This dataset compilation is provided "as is" without warranty of any kind, express or implied.
The dataset contains student writings from Turkish 101 and 102 courses (2014-2025)
that were originally published publicly by Bilkent University.

The original creative content was authored by Bilkent University students and instructors.
This project's contribution is the systematic collection, processing, and structuring 
of publicly available content for research purposes.

The compiler makes no representations about the suitability of this dataset for any purpose.
In no event shall the compiler be liable for any damages arising from the use of this dataset.
